## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and reports, which may not capture the full scope of changes in international business post-COVID-19. The rapidly evolving nature of global trade and business strategies means that new developments may not be fully reflected in the current analysis. Additionally, the lack of specific data from certain regions or industries may limit the generalizability of the findings.